    "enDesc": "Ein HaTekhelet is a work by the Radziner Rebbe (Rabbi Gershon Henoch Leiner) responding to questions and criticisms of his treatise “Treasures Hidden in the Sand,” in which he advocated searching for the source of tekhelet. Ein HaTekhelet was published after the Radziner Rebbe’s death.",
